9\" class=\"v31_1_19\">19</sup>Those of the Negeb shall possess Mount Esau,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v31_1_19\">and those of the Shephelah shall possess the land of the Philistines;</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v31_1_19\">they shall possess the land of Ephraim and the land of Samaria,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v31_1_19\">and Benjamin shall possess Gilead.</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v31_1_20\"><sup id=\"Obad.1.20\" class=\"v31_1_20\">20</sup>The exiles of this host of the people of Israel</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v31_1_20\">shall possess the land of the Canaanites as far as Zarephath,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v31_1_20\">and the exiles of Jerusalem who are in Sepharad</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v31_1_20\">shall possess the cities of the Negeb.</span></p>\n<p class=\"q1\"><span class=\"v31_1_21\"><sup id=\"Obad.1.21\" class=\"v31_1_21\">21</sup>Saviors shall go up to Mount Zion</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v31_1_21\">to rule Mount Esau,</span></p>\n<p class=\"q2\"><span class=\"v31_1_21\">and the kingdom shall be the <span class=\"nd\">Lord</span>\u2019s.</span></p>\n</div>\n", 
